      "content": "thanks. i'm kinda worried though because my chest feels a bit tight too. like i can't get a full breath in. but i dont want to go to the doctor if i dont have to, it's such a hassle. would an extra dose of the antihistamine help with the tightness, or should i just wait it out?",
